  <p><ul>
   <li>After breakfast, start for Solang Valley.</li>
   <li>Solang Valley is a side valley at the top of the Kullu valley in Himachal Pradesh. It is known for its summer and winter sports conditions. The sports most commonly offered are Ropeway, parachuting, paragliding, skating and zorbing. Snow melts during the summer months starting in May, and skiing is then replaced by zorbing.</li>
   <li> Dinner & overnight stay in Manali.</li>
 </ul>
 
 </p>
 </details>
