     <li> Head to Manikaran.</li>
     <li>Manikaran is located in the Parvati Valley between the rivers Vyaas and Parvati in the Kullu district of Himachal Pradesh. The hot water springs of Manikaran are famous across the country for their healing properties. The water temperature is more than the boiling point, making it possible to boil rice, pulses etc., in it.</li>
